(define/contract (min-operations s1 s2 x)
  (-> string? string? exact-integer? exact-integer?)
  (let ([n (string-length s1)]
        [cost 0]
        [i 0]
        [mismatches '()])
    ;; Iterate through both strings to identify mismatches
    (for ([i (in-range n)])
      (when (not (= (char->integer (string-ref s1 i))
                    (char->integer (string-ref s2 i))))
        (set! mismatches (cons i mismatches))))
    ;; Process mismatches to calculate the cost
    (let loop ([mismatches mismatches])
      (cond
       [(null? mismatches) cost]
       [(null? (cdr mismatches)) -1] ;; Odd number of mismatches
       [(= 1 (abs (- (car mismatches) (cadr mismatches)))) ;; Adjacent mismatches
        (begin
          (set! cost (+ cost 1))
          (loop (cddr mismatches)))]
       [else ;; Non-adjacent mismatches
        (begin
          (set! cost (+ cost x))
          (loop (cdr mismatches)))]))
    ))
